1. *Prekrasno* je videti kako se priroda budi u proleće. (It's *wonderful* to see how nature wakes up in spring.)
2. Videla sam *prekrasnu* haljinu u izlogu prodavnice. (*Beautiful* dress I saw in the store window.)
3. Večeras smo imali *prekrasan* koncert u operi. (Tonight we had a *gorgeous* concert at the opera.)
4. *Prekrasni* ljudi su nas dočekali u tom selu. (*Lovely* people greeted us in that village.)
5. Ova knjiga ima *prekrasan* kraj. (This book has a *wonderful* ending.)
6. Oni su se upoznali na *prekrasnom* letovanju na moru. (They met on a *beautiful* summer vacation by the sea.)
7. Hvala ti na *prekrasnom* poklonu, jako sam ga zavolela. (Thank you for the *amazing* gift, I really love it.)
8. Ova slika izgleda *prekrasno* u ovom okviru. (This picture looks *beautiful* in this frame.)
9. *Prekrasno* veče je bilo u gradu kada su slavili pobedu. (*Wonderful* evening in the city when they celebrated the victory.)
10. Uživao sam u *prekrasnom* pejzažu tokom svog odmora u prirodi. (I enjoyed the *gorgeous* scenery during my nature vacation.)